This folder holds raw candidate documents for the prompt optimisation tournament.
Add .txt files here — one file per document (CV, Arbeitszeugnis, certificate, etc.).
All files in this folder are gitignored. They never enter version control.

NAMING CONVENTION
  01-cv.txt                  primary CV text
  02-zeugnis-firma-x.txt     Arbeitszeugnis from Firma X
  03-zeugnis-firma-y.txt     Arbeitszeugnis from Firma Y
  04-certificate-aws.txt     certificate text
  05-notes.txt               any additional candidate notes

The tournament runner reads all .txt files in alphabetical order and
concatenates them into one raw record — no filtering, no AI processing.
